# OBJECT::DISABLE_TIDYING_UP_IN_GARAGE

## Summary
Enables/Disables tidying up (removing vehicle wrecks) in the garage

## Parameters
* **INT** garageHash
* **BOOL** disable

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Sets a flag. A valid id is 0x157DC10D
